T02D2365:8a-1: kye yul rnams thams cad lta 'dod na //
T02D2365:8b-0: ri @8b po chen po'i kha nas ltos //
T02D2365:8b-1: chos rnams thams cad skye 'gag med //
T02D2365:8b-2: rang sems rig nang rab rtse //
T02D2365:8b-4: rgya mtsho chen po'i chu la 'thung //
T02D2365:8b-5: skye med byang chub sems kyi chu //
T02D2365:8b-6: mtha' dbus mad pa'i rgya mtsho che //
T02D2365:8b-7: brtan g-yo thams cad bsreg 'dod na //
T02D2365:8b-8: 'jig pa'i dus kyi me chen spor //
T02D2365:8b-9: rnam rtog brtan g-yo thams cad de //
T02D2365:8b-10: lhun grub ye shes sems kyi me //
T02D2365:8b-12: dgon pa chen po'i gnas su 'dug /'khor ba rnam dag bde ba'i gnas //
T02D2365:8b-13: byang chub sems ni dgon pa che //
